ArcelorMittal South Africa Lifts Speciality Steel Prices 4.5%

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-05-03T11:55:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-03/arcelormittal-south-africa-plans-to-increase-speciality-steel-prices-4-5-.html
ArcelorMittal (MT)  South Africa Ltd. said
it will lift prices on a “small proportion” of speciality
long-steel products by 4.5 percent from June.  All prices were unchanged in May, the company said in an e-
mailed response to a query today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  